The '''worker caste''' was the largest caste among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Despite their size, they were the lowest caste. Workers included Yuuzhan Vong born as workers, those who failed in other castes, the [[Shamed Ones]], and [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]]. Some had a little honor, but most were looked on in contempt by the [[Warrior caste|warriors]] and the [[Intendant caste|intendants]].

Eventually, the workers joined the Shamed Ones in revolt against [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] and the [[Elite (Yuuzhan Vong)|Elite]].

